                     <locus from="2r" to="22r">2r-22r</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s34IHA">قران, Twenty seventh ǧuz’ (27/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#2r">-2r</locus>؟يها المرسلون , قالو انا ارسلنا [.؟.] مجرمين , لنرسل عليهم حجارة [.؟.] مسومة عند ربك للمسرفين<note>Beginnings of the lines covered by repair paper.</note>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#22r">-22r</locus>ان الفضل بيد الله يؤتيه من يشا والله ذوا الفضل العظيم</explicit>
                     <note>51:31-57:29. Words written in larger hand and traced in red on folios 11r and18r. Ornate rendition of letter ḥā' on fol. 5v and letter ayn on fol. 8v. Beginnings of the lines covered by repair paper on fol. 2r.</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
